  "commit_message": "chore(activations): remove invocation_type from Attachment and state.json (#4338)\n\n## Proposed Changes\n\n`invocation_type` was added to the `Attachment` struct in PR #4248\n(DEV-78)\nso it would be persisted in `state.json`. However, it was never read\nback\nat runtime — activation always receives it as a live parameter from the\nCLI, and `_FLOX_INVOCATION_TYPE` is available via the shell env during\ndeactivate. Persisting the field served no purpose. PR #4329 already\nreverted the underscore serializat",
